-!- FUNCTION: This protein catalyzes the inversion of a 3000-bp
    segment of phage DNA. The inversion results in a modification of
    the 3'-end of the tail fiber gene and alters the host specificity.
-!- SIMILARITY: Belongs to the site-specific recombinase resolvase
    family.
